                          <PhysicalContent xsi:type="MyObjectBuilder_Datapad">
                            <SubtypeName>Datapad</SubtypeName>
                            <Name>Fusion reacivity. </Name>
                            <Data>I dont know how they got ahold of something like this, or where they found this thing but this tech is increadible. 

This tech from the Data I've gleaned from the local servers is amazing. Its outputting 400Mw and it seems they also have some sort of high capacity batteries.

if we can get our hands on this it would be a massive change to our company and we could finally pull ahead of GC.

-A friend</Data>
